text: Ærest of Harandune wege ðonne hit sticað on Middelhæma gemæra on Suttuninga lace.
Of Suttuninga lace on Leofsiges gemæra on ða hnottan dic.
Of ðære hnottan dic on brembel þorn.
Of brembel þorne on Hengestes geat.
Of Hencstes geate on ða ealdan dune to Brihtwoldes gemæra.
Of Brihtwoldes gemæra æft on Harandune.
Ðis is ðara XVII hida land boc æt Harewylle ðe æðelred cing gebocode æðelricæ his þegne on ece yrfæ.
